title: [LFT] Gold II Top. Mid or Jungle Fill.
body: G'day, I'm Dave and I am currently looking to join a team to play ranked 5's. I am gold II and I mainly play top, but I can fill mid or jungle. I'm just looking for a bit of fun with mates, nothing extremely serious. Get back to me on here on just add me on league should you have any inquiries.

replies.body: hey I currently have a Silver team I'm looking to get back up and running add me in game if your interested you would be the top laner
